{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"1137-chandre-aani-champe","title":"चंद्र आनी चेपें","description":"वत आसता तेन्ना तुमकां चेपें घालपाक आवडटा व्हय? आनी कोणा-कोणाक चेपें घालपाक आवडटा तें पळोवया ह्या सोबीतश्या पुस्तकांत.\r\n","language":"Konkani","langCode":"kok","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Palia","Tanvi"],"illustrators":["Angie & Upesh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"World Konkani Centre","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/1137-chandre-aani-champe"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700911/size3/a7997747b4c2afe36ad258eb24979534.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700911/size6/a7997747b4c2afe36ad258eb24979534.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2789/size6/aaabacbf8e365331cc12d5c6d1166426.jpg","text":"आमी\nसगले दसऱ्याच्या जात्रेक\nगेल्ले.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2790/size6/cc128b0eba6ee81ca35645633730dc40.jpg","text":"पापान\nचिंटूक चकचकीत वक्ल घेतलें.\nआईन\nम्हाका एक निळें चेपें घेतलें.\nबायक\nसाकरे भोबो मेळ्ळो.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2791/size6/71d6d252238a3ceb3948291ba2865fad.jpg","text":"घरा\nवतना वाटेर नेटान वारें\nआयलें.\nम्हजें\nचेपें उडून गेलें.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2792/size6/08a18c29e1aff75deb9416131409b928.jpg","text":"म्हजें\nचेपें पोन्न्या पिंपळाच्या\nरुखाक शिरकलें.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2793/size6/cbb7590914f9a56a1e420873d491a8cf.jpg","text":"हांव\nखूब्ब रडलों.\nआनी\nहांव रातीं जेवलों ना.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2794/size6/30c5a5325f67da008f08afe0d26b3d15.jpg","text":"उपरांत\nते रातीं,\nचंद्र\nउदेलो.\nताणे\nपोन्न्या पिंपळाच्या रुखार\nम्हजें चेपें पळयलें.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2795/size6/698b1c39dee9c67c31d1eb2bbc86a603.jpg","text":"ताणें\nम्हजें चेपें घालून पळयलें.\nचंद्र\nखोशायेन हांसलो.\nम्हाकाय\nहांसचे पडलें.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2796/size6/a923f4c88afca7f7f21bd661a5f57f63.jpg","text":"दुसरे\nदिसा शाळा सुट्टकच म्हजे आवयन\nम्हाका एक\nचकचकीत नवेंताल्ल तांबडे\nचेपें दिलें. “चंद्रान\nधाडलां तें,”\nतिणे\nम्हळें.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2797/size6/70673625fc413701734cc82521eb0ce9.jpg","text":"ते\nरातीं,\nचंद्रान\nआनी हांवें दोगांयनी आमचीं\nचेपीं घालीं आनी हांसले.\nआमी\nखोशी आसले.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2798/size6/43a09a01293fed4b7626ce466ed01489.jpg","text":"सुर्याक\nचेपें जाय अशें तुमकां दिसता\nव्हय?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2799/size6/7db264d4d80d4c90b80894f15d14e1da.jpg","text":"हांवे\nआज कसलें चेपें घालां ते वळखात!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":113}}